  "detailed_description": "This is a thrilling 3D virtual VR game; the dragon knight is trapped in the castle while exploring,<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455190/extras/a2925d0a19f0276abf507bff445eb505.avif?t=1689234319\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>The dragon knight's dinosaur mount and the group tried to save it, but the hole was too small to do anything, so they could only circle around to guard against it.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2455190/extras/f53cc6b6db2a9d31a4cac1edf01a93b2.avif?t=1689234319\" width=600 height=336 /></span><br>Dragon Rider escapes the castle with a thrilling rock climb to rendezvous with the dinosaur mount.<br><br>Instructions:<br>Grab: Left/Right Gamepad Trigger<br>Position: left hand grip button<br>Walking: left handle up/down/left/right<br>Steering: right handle left/right",
